==English==
===Noun===
'''tonne'''

#A [[metric]] unit of mass equal to 1000 [[kilogram]]s.  Symbol: t

====Usage note====
*A tonne is approximately equal to a [[ton]] and the difference is not usually important.  However, because "tonne" is pronounced identically to "ton", there may be confusion when the word is spoken.  This may be avoided by using "metric ton" where "tonne" is intended.

